Kimberly S. Bartholomew
Assistant Vice President

Ms. Bartholomew is an Assistant Vice President of Crescent Capital Group LP focusing on investor relations. Prior to joining the team in 2007, Ms. Bartholomew was the Office Manager with Jensen Law Office, PLLC. Ms. Bartholomew received a BA from the University of Washington.

