Crescent Capital Group, LP Key Developments

Crescent Capital Group, LP Presents at Institutional and Alternative Lending Conference New York 2017, Jun-27-2017 02:00 PM
Jun 18 17
Crescent Capital Group, LP Presents at Institutional and Alternative Lending Conference New York 2017, Jun-27-2017 02:00 PM. Venue: New York, New York, United States. Speakers: John S. Bowman, Managing Director of Direct Lending.


Crescent Capital Group, LP Presents at The 20th Annual Milken Institute Global Conference, May-02-2017 02:30 PM
Apr 13 17
Crescent Capital Group, LP Presents at The 20th Annual Milken Institute Global Conference, May-02-2017 02:30 PM. Venue: The Beverly Hilton, 9876 Wilshire Boulevard, Beverly Hills, CA 90210, California, United States. Speakers: Steven Koehler, Senior Vice President of Capital Markets.


Crescent Capital Group Announces Hiring of Kenneth McRay and Glynell Bradley as Senior Vice Presidents in Investor Relations
Apr 5 17
Crescent Capital Group LP announced that Kenneth McRay and Glynell Bradley have joined the company as Senior Vice Presidents in Investor Relations. Mr. McRay will focus on expanding the firm’s business development efforts across institutional investors, and Mr. Bradley will further enhance Crescent Capital’s relationships with consultants and gatekeepers. Mr. McRay brings more than 20 years of experience in the financial industry. He joins Crescent Capital from Pinebridge Investments where he was a Senior Vice President in Institutional Sales and Marketing. Prior to that, he was Vice President at Deutsche Bank and also served at Rogerscasey and Ernst & Young. Mr. Bradley has 15 years of experience in institutional sales. He previously spent his career at Goldman Sachs, rising to become Vice President of U.S. Institutional Sales-Consultant Relations prior to joining Crescent Capital.


